{"tid":2096020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世貿前逃生避過911襲擊 著名新聞圖片人物死於武肺","createTime":"2020-07-06T01:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T02:02:22.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f71bf5f0ad8aab4441a7667cf565b1d39c4d30f2","tid":2096020,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/olSOyQj1PrB2ULVd0FcKhdpmcdg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N4MWXHVNZ5IQIZU7JM2T5KCZW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FolSOyQj1PrB2ULVd0FcKhdpmcdg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN4MWXHVNZ5IQIZU7JM2T5KCZW4.jpg&h=d6c9fe13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n庫珀（左）手抱公文袋逃生，成為經典新聞圖片的一角。<br />\n(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國一名911生還者庫珀（Stephen Cooper）在3月28日於佛羅里達州因武漢肺炎不治，終年78歲。當年他被美聯社記者拍到在正倒下的世貿大厦前，與其他人在瓦礫四散和漫天灰塵的災難之中，夾着公文袋逃生，立下歷史存照，成為最多人看過的新聞圖片之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200705/YW5VFMQYLOE4HD4D7RRIE32TNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200705%2FYW5VFMQYLOE4HD4D7RRIE32TNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=f120a3b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200705%2FYW5VFMQYLOE4HD4D7RRIE32TNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0ebe7853\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200705/YW5VFMQYLOE4HD4D7RRIE32TNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=s